= h1  ourbigbook
== h2 1 quick-start
== h2 2 design-goals
=== h3 2.1 saner
=== h3 2.2 more-powerful
== h2 3 paragraphs
== h2 4 links
``

This option can also serve as a debug tool for header tree related features (confession: that was its original motivation!).

